      <title>尽管需求驱动因素参差不齐，但油价上涨，市场仍在等待 OPEC+ 的决定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-rise-gaza-deaths-complicate-ceasefire-talks-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国和中国主要消费者的需求指标不同，市场等待欧佩克+就第二季度供应协议做出决定，油价周五小幅上涨，预计本周小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-rise-gaza-deaths-complicate-ceasefire-talks-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 02:26:52 GMT</pubDate>
